result.name: Law Mark Kee, Hysan Place

reviews.text: Nice restaurant. Good food. Not perfect (had better fried noodle with beef, but the curry chicken rice was better!) Enjoyable experience.
An authentic Hong Kong style cafe that serves competitive lunch menu. If you like spicy food you should try this restaurant.

If you are looking for some traditional local Hong Kong food, look no further. This restaurant, located on the top floor of the Hysan Place offers variety of choices from toast to instant noodles to desserts (black bull - coke with chocolate ice cream) that are authentic and at an affordable price.

Came by with a friend who recommended this place for its authentic Hong Kong dishes. It wasn't too difficult to find since it was at the top floor or Hysan Place. It wasn't too busy so we didn't have to wait for a table.
We ordered a few things to share. The beef noodles were really tasty as was the BBQ pork fried rice. The most interesting dish was the giant toast. It was literally half a loaf of bread with a soft shell crab on top smothered with curry sauce. The surprising thing was that it was filled with delicious fried rice. That in itself was a meal and a half.
Really nice place with really nice food which is apparently very busy during lunch.
Classic bing sutt style hk cafe.  US equivalent to a very elevated Mel's.  Highly recommend the milk tea with red bean!

result.name: 羅麥記

reviews.text: 用了團購劵超抵食。裝修懷舊有睇頭。鋪面很大但滿座率超高。食物款式多且好味，芝士撈丁，磚頭焗飯等等都是該店推介菜式。不過在商場14樓有點不便，去餐廳很費時。

Authentic HK style milk tea.. half tomatoes and half creamy white sauce with king prawns fired rice, and prawn toast.  Lot of local dishes to try, nice services, waiting time was reasonable, open till late to 22:30. Would definitely come often to try everything.
味道不好 🙁 ；但懷舊茶餐廳環境不錯。雖然叫了「招牌推介」的羅麥雞翼撈通粉（加辣），但那只是甜豉油汁，而且超級甜，甜到好似甜品！非常不行 👎🏼👎🏼👎🏼 ，雞翼還可以。

出到黎CWB想搵個舒服又唔高消費既地方，真係唔易，今日朋友話有間餐廳係希慎，食野唔洗加一...聽到心諗，唔洗加一都唔會平得去邊!!!不過是旦喇，出黎食個飯，冇4百都要3百既...

點知一黎到，睇佢地第一頁既menu價錢平到你唔信...唔講咁多，睇左先~!

咁抵食，唔理咁多喇!!!黎兩杯特飲透心涼下先~!

呢個雞翼都幾大隻，同埋好入味，雞肉都好嫩滑，好味~!

而呢個避風堂豬頸肉撈面，有小小干身，但豬頸肉夠哂大塊，一個人食就好快會食飽
鴛鴦飯！  炒底，不油膩。 白汁除了大大隻蝦碌，還有我喜愛的脆玉瓜粒。紅汁酸甜適中。
